Click here for our Event Planning Guide
A beautiful place to host your special 
        event.
River Palm Cottages & Fish Camp 
            is a great place for :
- Birthday Parties
- Anniversaries
- Weddings
- Class Reunions
- Family Reunions
- Small Business Seminars
Our facilities provide the relaxed 
            atmosphere to accommodate any event!
For intimate parties of 10 up to 250!
Daily Rate
(includes 
            setup time for tents, tables, etc)
Fri, Sat, Sun $1,250.00
Mon - Thurs $625.00
Deposit
(upon cancellation, balance due 30 days prior to function)
50%
Cancellations
(for any chickee hut reservation cancellation within 60 days of scheduled event)
50%
Cancellations
(cancellation fee will be charged for any chickee hut contract cancellation)
25%
Parking
(parking 
            attendant supplied by River Palm - will direct guests to
            appropriate area)
Attendant is mandatory for functions with over 50 guests. Optional 
            valet parking may be contracted by guest. Small event parking shall 
            be on North Lot.
1st hour ........
$75.00
ea add hr ........
$25.00
Would you like River Palm to Organize Your 
            Function?
Facility Service Fee
(Fee applied 
            for all functions organized by River Palm management. We will make 
            all of your arrangements from catering, tent rental, music, etc.)
15%
Clean Up Fee / Damage Fee
(Set 
            Up and Clean Up must be completed within Rental time frame)
applied accordingly
Minimum Stay
2 night minimum stay on weekends
3 night minimum stay on holidays
